{"tid":1076363,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱有個一畢業就個個月去旅行既舊同學喊哂口問我借錢","createTime":"2019-03-24T19:30:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T06:20:52.000Z","uid":78947,"like":27,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"70d2d92567e667369973a20e9b3631649c6b8c87","tid":1076363,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T19:30:45.000Z","msg":"我地畢左業一段時間，大家都有每年keep著食飯。<br />\n<br />\n近期佢話想借一筆錢去私家醫院做手術，因為佢自己儲蓄唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然十萬八萬對我現在來講唔係大數目，但我一口拒絕左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 「屌你老母x年前個個月去旅行咁撚風光，有冇人可憐我朝七晚七，日日比老闆鬧？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n望著佢死死氣排公立個撚頭樣，開始覺得後生時辛苦d積榖防餓都係值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae53c2269e94dd9f1963c9673aff1f1f5d2d956","tid":1076363,"uid":236401,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T19:34:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"28dc9c44a63925a57bbc68a48fa5a05448fe436b","tid":1076363,"uid":178800,"like":43,"dislike":15,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T19:39:31.000Z","msg":"你留意番自己語氣<br />\n你已經係廢老口吻了<br />\n你可以返FACEBOOK耀武揚威了<br />\n呢度唔岩你了"},{"pid":"2ac5a97e921d117fc5e55d647b68c013c33c2215","tid":1076363,"uid":14908,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T19:51:12.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗開2個post講壞話，唔借咪唔借"},{"pid":"4d9240941d5872c3dbae706c1f4f5bf57d26a6d2","tid":1076363,"uid":101823,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"28dc9c44a63925a57bbc68a48fa5a05448fe436b","tid":1076363,"uid":178800,"like":43,"dislike":15,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T19:39:31.000Z","msg":"你留意番自己語氣<br />\n你已經係